NO BANK QUALIFING!  $37,000 DOWN AND ASSUME LOAN WILL GET YOU A BEAUTIFUL 2 HOMES LOCATED ON 10 ACRES CORNER LOT THAT IS FENCED AND READY FOR LIVESTOCK. MAIN HOUSE IS APPROX 2700 SQ FT WITH 2 LIVING AREAS, 2 MAIN BEDROOMS BOTH WITH FULL BATHS AND WALK-IN CLOSETS, PLUS 2 ADDITIONAL BEDROOMS AND FULL BATH. THE 2ND HOUSE IS APPROX 1100 SQ FT WITH 2 beds 
And 2 BATHS . PROPERTY ALSO INCLUDES A LARGE BARN AND SHED.  $390,000 is total payoff in assuming loan. I can also do a Short Sale . Short sale has been approved at $330 000. TIME IS OF THE ESSENCE!
             BUY A HOUSE WITHOUT WORRYING ABOUT A CREDIT SCORE!
THE ADDRESS OF THE SMALL HOUSE IS 11058 N COUNTY RD 3200 , PAOLI OK 73074.
WITH GPS HOME IS EASIER TO FIND WITH THIS ADDRESS!
